@NODE "History" "History"





                                 HISTORY



 version 1.1  (Oct 15 1995) : - My version for personal use...
                            

 version 1.2  (Nov 03,1995) : - Beta version to gauge response to see
                                if futher development would be welcomed.

 version 1.3 - 3.21 (Nov 03,1995 - Feb 21,1996) : - Complete Re-Write to
		make it workbench 2 compatible and added Tooltype support.
		History list view window, Keyboard shortcuts.

 version 3.24 (Feb 23,1996) : - Added Quit yes or No requester to keyboard
				shortcut and Quit button. Getnews and Prepnews
				now configable via ToolTypes.

 version 3.25 (Feb 25,1996) : - Added Quit requester too the close window
				Gadget.

 version 3.26 (Mar 04,1996) : - Added ToolType support for StartNet and
				StopNet.

 version 3.27 (Mar 05,1996) : - Added 2nd ListView (Not working yet)

 version 3.28 (Mar 06,1996) : - Added ToolType support to disable quit
				requestor.

 version 3.29 (Mar 07,1996) : - Changed a few tooltypes and button locations.

 version 3.30 (Mar 07,1996) : - Internal mod's.

 version 3.31 (Mar 08,1996) : - Tidy'ed up the buttons.

 version 3.32 (Mar 08,1996) : - Got second listview too work partially.

 version 3.33 (Mar 09,1996) : - Got output of startnet to go too listview2.

 version 3.34 - 3.35 (Mar 09,1996) : - Got all ouput to go too listview2.

 version 3.36 (Mar 10,1996) : - Fixed bug in listview that double printed
 				last line of message.

 version 3.37 (Mar 13,1996) : - Added test to make sure that had been run
 				from the Workbench and not via Shell/Cli.

 version 3.38 (Mar 13,1996) : - Added Arexx Ports 1 & 2 and added the
 				Arexx function commands.

 version 3.39 (Mar 14,1996) : - Changed the GetNews keyboard shortcut too
                                g as it should have been.

 version 3.40 (Mar 19,1996) : - Made the Gui window a bit wider.
				Changed the No requester tooltype from
				REQUESTER too NOREQUESTER

 version 3.41 (Mar 26,1996) : - Fixed bug that would not allow larger than
                                9 point Fonts.

 version 3.42 (Mar 27,1996) : - Fixed bug that printed Quit half underneath
                                the GetNews button.

