@NODE "SystemReq" "System Requirements"





                            SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS



             To use NetFace you will need the folling set-up.

                 - An Amiga with Kickstart 2.0 or higher.

                        - WorkBench 2.1 or higher.

           May work with Workbench 2.04 but has not been tested
           if you are using Workbench 2.04 please let me know if
           it works ok.




                                 TESTED ON

      

                A4000 030, Gvp Scsi Board, 514 Mb Hd, Cdrom
                2 Mb Chip, 12 Mb Fast Ram, 1 Gig Ide Hd.

                A4000 040, 2 Mb Chip, 8 Mb Fast Ram.

                A4000 060. 

                A2000, 1 Mb Chip, 6 Mb Fast, Kickstart Workbench 3.1,
                Gvp Scsi Board, 512 Mb Hard drive, Cdrom.

                A2000 1 Mb Chip, 4 Mb Fast, Kickstart Workbench 3.1,
                Gvp 030 Scsi Board, 378 Mb Hard Drive, Cdrom.

                A1200, 030-50mhz, 2 Mb Chip, 8 Mb Fast,
                Scsi II 1700 mb Hard drive, 3 * Cdrom.

                A500, 3 mb Ram, 120 mb hard drive, Cdrom.




